data.description: Unlock the Door to Your Dream home for sale in the heart Jarrell, TX. Custom upgrades, granite countertops, kitchen island and breakfast dining area just off the kitchen. There is a formal dining room that can be used for a study or an extra bedroom. There is a built in Murphy bed ready for any overnight guests.  The main bedroom has a walk-in two head shower and a bathtub along with a double vanity. Wood grain tile throughout the house that give this home a high-end look. On the other side of the house are two bedroom that share a full bath with double vanity. The backyard is a good size, covered patio for your outdoor retreat.
